      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. This car shows its age and is best suited for a buyer seeking practical value, a work commuter, or a project opportunity. Priced to reflect condition while still presenting a cost-effective way to get on the road.",
